  <h1 class="logo">CareerWiz</h1>
  <p>CareerWiz is the one-stop solution for all your career guidance needs.
    Explore courses available after intermediate. You can get counselling from
    experts regarding your career path and get the latest updates about
    college admissions and related.
  </p>
  <p>Watch this video to know more:
    <video src="Counselling.mp4" controls>
    </video>
  </p>
  <h2>Choosing a Career</h2>
  <p>So what are the factors to consider?<br />
  Before you make a choice analyze what it is you would like to do.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Assess your capability, interest and personality either yourself or by visiting a career-counselor.</li>
    <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Based on your interests make a list of careers keeping in mind your personality and abilities.</li>
    <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Explore all the careers in your list. Do a detailed research on the job profiles, requirements, prospects, how to develop your career.</li>
    <li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Once you're done with the above, pick the one that suits you the most.</li>

  </ul>
</article>
